snippet.title: WAR Pig Big Bang Gameplay (PC game)
snippet.description:
WAR Pig Big Bang PC Gameplay (Computer game): Adventure, Indie
Download In Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/736610/WAR_Pig__Big_Bang/
About WAR Pig Big Bang :
Your mission is easy: Destroy the enemy! That is all - no more, no less. Fight your way through many exciting missions in the campaign or compete against each other with up to 6 teams, consisting of 6 pigs each in free play mode. 
Subscribe for see more videos here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmk_1iK7Dxd2VmIo1DwN0cw
